#if needed softwares is not installed,install them
#create task dir, create task script using templates and task configure file
#task configure file include: 
#(1) task command, ping <target>, <target> could be a variable read
#(2) <target> or <target_list> filename
#(3) <prober-list> 
#(4) avoid-flooding options,may include:minimize,random,round-robin
#(5) crontab configuration for the task
#(6) output format, usually located in data/taskname/yy/mm/dd/data_hh_mm_ss
#    or data/taskname/yy/mm/data_dd(daily data)
#(7) analysis scripts
#usage make_task task_config_file
